        public static Release parseItem(net.mircomacrelli.rss.Item item,
                java.lang.String tkSource)
                         throws java.lang.Exception
        Create a release for an item of a RSS feed and a tracker name.
        Parameters:
        item - Item of a RSS feed, it contains at least the complete name of the release and a UTC date.
        tkSource - Name of the tracker of origin.
        Returns:
        Release representing the parsed information.
        Throws:
